<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      strong {
        color: #000000;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777777;
        margin-top: 40px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        padding-top: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Congratulations, <%= @tirador.profile.first_name.strip %>!</h1>

      <p>You have received a new hiring request from <strong><%= @client_name %></strong>.</p>

      <p>Job Title: <strong><%= @tirador.profile.more_info.active_service %></strong></p>

      <p>You can contact the client directly at: <strong><%= @client_mobile %></strong>.</p>

      <p>We wish you the best of luck with your new Tirada!</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br/>
        The Tiirada Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
